{"tid":757390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國淡化處理美國駐京大使館外爆炸案","createTime":"2018-07-26T21:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T03:02:43.000Z","uid":147314,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b4a2f78a8b42df91f21fc3df96937c754fa5c23e","tid":757390,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T21:38:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/cantonese-web-news-china-us-embassy-explosion-20180726-ry/4501105.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fcantonese-web-news-china-us-embassy-explosion-20180726-ry%2F4501105.html&d=YDpFvmEDpF5LG4WvhAwVkS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=fdb08f6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/cantonese-web-news-china-us-embassy-explosion-20180726-ry/4501105.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中國淡化處理美國駐京大使館外爆炸案</strong><br />\n<br />\n2018年7月27日<br />\n美國之音粵語組<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/DF1D60D6-E094-4BF6-B731-C444D6EC67D7_w1023_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2FDF1D60D6-E094-4BF6-B731-C444D6EC67D7_w1023_r1_s.jpg&h=8343af92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">在美國駐北京大使館外爆炸地點附近的中國警察</span><br />\n<br />\n華盛頓 &mdash; <br />\n中國當局說，在美國駐華大使館附近7月26日星期四下午發生的爆炸案，姓姜的涉案者有精神病。<br />\n<br />\n北京市公安局在星期四晚上的一則微博中說，2016年下半年開始，姓姜的涉案者經常出現幻聽幻覺，曾去醫院住院治療並且接受心理輔導，之後一直無法正常工作。這則微博還說，警方調取了醫院的診療記錄，姓姜的涉案者被診斷為偏執型人格障礙。<br />\n<br />\n現場傳出的視頻和照片顯示，星期四的爆炸形成一團巨大煙霧。美國之音駐北京記者在現場實地採訪時發現，美國大使館大門口外路面上有一灘血跡，不遠處有碎玻璃散落地面。<br />\n<br />\n美國大使館官微證實了這宗爆炸案，稱一名人士引爆的是&ldquo;炸彈&rdquo;，但中國警方稱是&ldquo;疑似爆竹裝置&rdquo;。中國外交部發言人耿爽說，這是一宗孤立的治安事件。<br />\n<br />\n此外，包括在北京市公安局的微博在內，官方只提及事發地區的路名，只說是在朝陽區天澤路和安家樓路的路口，避免提及美國駐中國大使館。而美國大使館則指出，事發地點在&ldquo;大使館建筑物東南角外的街道上&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n美國駐華大使館的地址為朝陽區安家樓路55號，距離天澤路和安家樓路十字路口只有幾十米。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/cantonese-web-news-china-us-embassy-explosion-20180726-ry/4500713.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fcantonese-web-news-china-us-embassy-explosion-20180726-ry%2F4500713.html&d=YDpFvmEDpF5LG4WvhAwVkS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=8fba735c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/cantonese-web-news-china-us-embassy-explosion-20180726-ry/4500713.html</a>"},{"pid":"dd5cd54ab21a5218f761fc9e25f7d55f2407bd28","tid":757390,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T23:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed79c28129d35d1a99370fe3358b527a312959f","tid":757390,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T23:16:57.000Z","msg":"越描越黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8a0f8c02fe69544452f2480533c40592df2a88","tid":757390,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T23:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冷處理"},{"pid":"f806fa3602f835f4d0631bb9bf9d85d69ff9076f","tid":757390,"uid":104699,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:05:24.000Z","msg":"內外交困，有人想幫習仔同侵開戰"},{"pid":"d4cf2488c693fdfe809da227609d0f47eef59146","tid":757390,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:15:08.000Z","msg":"邊有咁多癡線佬<br />\n<br />\n大陸成日想報<br />\n南斯拉夫大使館嘅仇"},{"pid":"7ad9f4b7e91fe9dfc78906bea3525b7c6d5c93b6","tid":757390,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:25:39.000Z","msg":"有精神病都做到個炸彈出來！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸又贏！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33696aa3cf6aaa5f5c7cf9f0c014e1bccd11aac","tid":757390,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T00:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d77943ba9fbca317e8f4a8b3f19ecabd8b02cc","tid":757390